In this section, we investigate ARoW algorithm in view of robustness and generalization by analyzing the four benchmark data sets - CIFAR10, CIFAR100 (
            , 
          ) , F-MINST (
            , 
          ) and SVHN dataset (
            , 
          ).
In particular, we show that ARoW is superior to existing algorithms including TRADES (
